502
00:39:11,276 --> 00:39:13,506
l have a mission.

503
00:39:13,596 --> 00:39:17,066
To win this war. To save the world.

504
00:39:18,316 --> 00:39:20,989
l don't have time for vendettas.

505
00:39:23,516 --> 00:39:26,314
